question: Query
sql:
SELECT p.Category, DATE_FORMAT(so.OrderDate, '%Y-%m') AS Month, COUNT(*) AS SalesCount
FROM products p JOIN orderitems oi ON p.ProductID = oi.ProductID JOIN salesorders so ON oi.OrderID = so.OrderID
WHERE YEAR(so.OrderDate) >= YEAR(CURDATE()) - 5
GROUP BY p.Category, Month
ORDER BY Category, Month

question: Query
sql:
SELECT Industry, AVG(TotalSales) AS Average_Sales FROM (
  SELECT c.Industry, so.TotalAmount AS TotalSales FROM customers c
  JOIN salesorders so ON c.CustomerID = so.CustomerID
  GROUP BY c.Industry
) AS industry_sales ORDER BY Average_Sales DESC

sql: SELECT CustomerName, ContactPerson, ContactEmail, PhoneNumber FROM customers WHERE ContactPerson = 'Aditi Kapoor'

question: Query
sql:
SELECT p.ProductName, SUM(oi.Quantity) AS TotalUnitsSold
FROM products p JOIN orderitems oi ON p.ProductID = oi.ProductID
WHERE oi.Quantity < 20
GROUP BY p.ProductName
